results.name: One-based column index to array A263255.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10002
program: (define (A263274 n) (let ((rowf (rowfun-for-A263255 (A263254 n)))) (let loop ((i 1)) (if (= n (rowf i)) i (loop (+ 1 i))))))
